是吸熱or放熱？2. 薄荷腦為何用礦物油研磨？3. 電熱包、水浴鍋的選擇？Methylcellulose 400cps             1 gCarbomer 934                    0.25 g Propylene glycol                     16 mLUrea                                     10 gPurified water                      100 mL-------------------------------------------------------1 N NaOH                        q.s. to pH 7Full transcriptMore presentations by
    
        
